      <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed italic">Dolphin Centrifuge supplies the Alfa Laval NX-314, a two-phase horizontal decanter centrifuge generating 3,157 Gs at 4,000 RPM with a 10 HP motor. Rated at 25 GPM for hemp ethanol slurry, it serves <a href="/wastewater-centrifuge/">wastewater dewatering</a>, <a href="/waste-oil-centrifuge/">waste oil de-sludging</a>, and industrial sludge separation applications.</p>
