    <h2 id="nx-314-overview">Alfa Laval NX 314 B31-G Two-Phase Decanter Centrifuge</h2>

    <img
      src="/images/alfa-laval-nx-314-decanter-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-Decanter-Centrifuge-System-Class-1-Div-2-for-Herbal-Extraction-600.webp"
