      height="600"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic mb-6 text-center">Alfa Laval Decanter Centrifuge System — Class 1 Div 2 for Herbal Extraction</p>

    <p>
      The Alfa Laval NX 314 <a href="/decanter-centrifuge/">Decanter Centrifuge</a> is a horizontal de-sludging centrifuge built for the two-phase separation of wastewater, crude oil tank bottoms, municipal sludge-thickening, industrial sludge dewatering, paint sludge handling, etc. With a 10 HP Motor, the NX 314 decanter has a bowl RPM of 4,000 and can process 25 GPM of ethanol hemp biomass slurry.
    </p>

    <p>
      The NX 314 is one of the most versatile decanter centrifuges in the Alfa Laval product line. Its compact 14-inch bowl diameter and 34-inch bowl length make it suitable for a wide range of industrial applications, from municipal <a href="/wastewater-centrifuge/">wastewater sludge dewatering</a> to edible oil desludging and waste oil recovery. Dolphin Centrifuge supplies fully reconditioned NX 314 decanter centrifuges with complete inspection, testing, and warranty coverage. Each unit undergoes thorough mechanical and process testing before delivery to ensure reliable performance in the field.
    </p>

