    <p>The Alfa Laval NX 314 decanter centrifuge is suited for a wide range of two-phase solid/liquid separation applications across multiple industries. Its robust construction and adjustable differential speed allow it to handle varying solids concentrations and fluid viscosities effectively.</p>
